				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-V%C5%A9-X%E1%BB%A9ng/C%E1%BA%A3m-l%C6%B0u-vong/poem-2eUGsCyGotGtviV5C0QIDw">Cảm lưu vong - 感流亡</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-V%C5%A9-X%E1%BB%A9ng/author-gsSbrX8mxDOHV8mbduxYMg">Vương Vũ Xứng</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C6%B0-M%C3%A3-T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Nh%C6%B0/C%E1%BA%A7m-ca-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-zuM8EVmyazH-Et0Vl_289g">Cầm ca kỳ 1 - 琴歌其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C6%B0-M%C3%A3-T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Nh%C6%B0/author-HC1oHxsir20vL_KcVXiEhQ">Tư Mã Tương Như</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/%C4%90%E1%BB%87-%C4%91%E1%BB%97-4/poem-JlpvkB5eRTk9D-axHhvYbg">Đệ đỗ 4 - 杕杜 4</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Vi%E1%BB%87t-Nam/%C4%90%E1%BB%95ng-H%E1%BB%93-b%C3%BAt-ph%C3%BA/poem-zjv_6tPCykW3dsLfeEVU1g">Đổng Hồ bút phú - 董狐筆賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Vi%E1%BB%87t-Nam/author-kBTBt5Mbi6PPrH2sJkQAPw">Khuyết danh Việt Nam</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/%C4%90%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-c%C3%BA-h%E1%BB%AFu-%C4%91%E1%BB%91i/poem-Us294ro5mSX1nPNOUKfyEw">Đương cú hữu đối - 當句有對</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/author-9iJ5oLtFQBkuT0Ej5xvn9Q">Lý Thương Ẩn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/Gi%E1%BA%A3-s%C6%A1n-thu%E1%BB%B7/poem-NKCGXUhoAMI7WQyLLfzZyA">Giả sơn thuỷ - 假山水</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%82u-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Qu%C3%BDnh/Hoa-gian-t%E1%BA%ADp-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-hcBoiNYYaGQbRGy48SZcuw">Hoa gian tập tự - 花間集敘<